    "body": "Been meaning to fix this for a while now. On many systems, envoking `vi` runs vim in compatibility-mode. Many of the vim commands you've come to know and love don't work and `~/.vimrc` doesn't get sourced. The new order of precedence is:\r\n\r\n1. `EDITOR`\r\n2. `vim`\r\n3. `vi`\r\n\r\n@JusticeForMikeBrown",
